            {
              "question": "当时区为GMT+08:00、CMOS时间为03:00时，Linux的显示时间是多少？",
              "id": "3-93-4",
              "answers": [
                {
                  "text": "11:00",
                  "answer_start": 82
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "context": "解决双系统时间不一致有两个办法：让Windows启用UTC；让Ubuntu禁用UTC，推荐第二种。",
          "qas": [
            {
              "question": "解决Linux&Windows双系统时间不一致的办法有哪些？",
              "id": "3-93-5",
              "answers": [
                {
                  "text": "让Windows启用UTC；让Ubuntu禁用UTC",
                  "answer_start": 30
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "question": "推荐哪种解决双系统时间不一致的办法？",
              "id": "3-93-6",
              "answers": [
                {
                  "text": "让Ubuntu禁用UTC",
                  "answer_start": 56
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "context": "Windows下启用UTC：Win+R打开运行，输入regedit启动注册表编辑器，找到HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE/SYSTEM/CurrentControlSet/Control/TimeZoneInformation/，添加REG_DWORD类型键值RealTimeIsUniversal，值为1，重启生效。",
          "qas": [
            {
              "question": "如何在Windows下启用UTC？",
              "id": "3-93-7",
              "answers": [
                {
                  "text": "Win+R打开运行，输入regedit启动注册表编辑器，找到HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE/SYSTEM/CurrentControlSet/Control/TimeZoneInformation/，添加REG_DWORD类型键值RealTimeIsUniversal，值为1，重启生效。",
                  "answer_start": 15
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "question": "在Windows启用UTC时，需添加的键值类型是什么？",
              "id": "3-93-8",
              "answers": [
                {
                  "text": "REG_DWORD",
                  "answer_start": 134
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "question": "Windows下启用UTC添加的键值名称和值分别是什么？",
              "id": "3-93-9",
              "answers": [
                {
                  "text": "名称为RealTimeIsUniversal，值为1",
                  "answer_start": 146
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
